<section>
  <h2>About the blog</h2>
  <p>
    This blog is built with the excellent <a href="https://www.11ty.dev/" target="_blank">Eleventy</a>, and hosted on
    GitHub Pages.
  </p>
  <p>
    Everything is proudly constructed with plain old web technology: hand-written HTML and CSS, with no frameworks and
    no client-side JavaScript. My goal is for the site to be fast, accessible, and privacy-preserving for everyone. It
    should look great in your browser’s reading mode, or your <a href="/feed.xml">RSS reader</a>. This website collects
    no analytics and stores no cookies.
  </p>
  <p>
    Most importantly: every word I write is my own thoughts, and every line of code committed is my own work. No LLMs,
    no slop, no engagement bait.
  </p>
